# Local sensitive patterns — one extended regex per line.
# Copy this file to patterns.local and populate with org-specific values.
# Lines starting with # are ignored. Blank lines are ignored.
# The pre-commit hook combines all lines into a single grep -iE pattern.
#
# Example entries:
# 123456789012
# myorg\.awsapps\.com
# InternalProjectName
# @mycompany\.com
